	* src/core/automation_editor.cpp:
	- work with inverted midi time
	- fixed display of hidden values
	- added red cross
	- update detuning in the piano roll
	- removed cursor enter/leave events, they could be ignored
	- optimized unsafe loops
	- minor optimizations

